          "cre": "2016-02-28T09:29:25",
          "mod": "2016-02-28T09:31:07",
          "lines": [
            0,
            58,
            119
          ],
          "text": "Orphaned photos (those without associated versions in the db) could also be detected in the Purge dialog. Instead of a checkbox, a radio group could be created:",
          "uuid": "c9ffc684"
        }
      ]
    },
